            <p>Para instalar JAVA8</p>
            <code>
              <p>cd /opt/
              </p>
              <p>wget download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/8u111-b14/jdk-8u111-linux-arm32-vfp-hflt.tar.gz</p>
