            <p>Para instalar <a href="http://orientdb.com/" target="_blank">OrientDB</a></p>
            <code>
              <p>cd /usr/share/
              </p>
              <p>wget http://orientdb.com/download.php?file=orientdb-community-2.2.14.tar.gz&amp;os=linux</p>
