              <p>rm orientdb-community-2.2.14.tar.gz</p>
              <p>cd /orientdb-community-2.2.14/bin</p>
            </code>
            <p>Editamos la linea del fichero server.sh</p>
            <code><p># Raspberry Pi check (Java VM does not run with -server argument on ARMv6)
                if [ `uname -m` != "armv7l" ]; then
                JAVA_OPTS="$JAVA_OPTS -server "
                fi
                export JAVA_OPTS</p>
              <p>sudo sh server.sh </p>

            </code>
            <p>* <a href="http://orientdb.com/docs/2.0/orientdb.wiki/Tutorial-Run-the-server.html" target="_blank">Documentación</a>
